headline.main: Sikhs Respond to Shooting Near Seattle With Fear, Disbelief
headline.print_headline: Sikhs Respond to Shooting Near Seattle With Fear, Disbelief

lead_paragraph: Fear, hurt and disbelief weighed on the minds of those who gathered at a Sikh temple Sunday after the shooting of a Sikh man who said a gunman approached him in his suburban Seattle driveway and told him "go back to your own country."
